            "title": "盤中速報 - 芯源系統(MPWR-US)大漲5.05%，報1051.99美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>芯源系統(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MPWR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MPWR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MPWR-US</a>)截至台北時間23日21:36股價上漲50.59美元，報1051.99美元，漲幅5.05%，成交量62,667（股），盤中最高價1051.99美元、最低價1038.60美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.05%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.19%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.05%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.51%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>芯源系統(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MPWR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MPWR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MPWR-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-0.65%</li> <li>近 1 月：+8.52%</li> <li>近 3 月：+39.09%</li> <li>近 6 月：+95.65%</li> <li>今年以來：+68.52%</li></ul></section></main>",
