        {
            "id": 6203062,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 費城半導體大漲1%，報6744.53點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間23日09:39，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>上漲66.96點（或1%），暫報6744.53點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：-1.32%</li><li>近 1 月：+5.49%</li><li>近 3 月：+18.42%</li><li>近 6 月：+74.26%</li><li>今年以來：+32.98%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>成分股以芯源系統(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MPWR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MPWR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MPWR-US</a>)領漲。芯源系統(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MPWR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MPWR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MPWR-US</a>)上漲4.86%；連貫(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:COHR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/COHR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">COHR-US</a>)上漲2.89%；Onto Innovation Inc.(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ONTO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ONTO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ONTO-US</a>)上漲2.6%；安可(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMKR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMKR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMKR-US</a>)上漲2.05%；泰瑞達(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TER:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TER\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TER-US</a>)上漲1.98%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>部分成分股表現相對疲軟，高通(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:QCOM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/QCOM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">QCOM-US</a>)下跌0.24%；英特爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTC-US</a>)下跌0.18%；凌雲邏輯(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CRUS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CRUS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CRUS-US</a>)下跌0.15%。</p></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6203062",
